  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12036882/same-jar-files-in-ejb-ear-project",
  "title" : "Same jar Files in EJB &amp; EAR project",
  "body" : "<p>How can I use the same jar files in EJB and EAR projects?</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>EJB</strong> ---> Jar files to add build path in Eclipse.</li>\n<li><strong>EAR</strong> ---> EJB project &amp; jar files to add Java EE dependencies.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Otherwise I'm getting a <strong><em>class cast Exception</em></strong> for what seems to be identical classes.</p>\n\n<p>Example:</p>\n\n<p>com.sample.es.ra.<strong>EsCciConnectionFactory</strong> cannot be cast to com.sample.es.ra.<strong>EsCciConnectionFactory</strong></p>\n"
}